ca.fwe.units
Class BaseUnit.Dimension

java.lang.Object
  ca.fwe.units.BaseUnit.Dimension
Enclosing class:
BaseUnit
public static class BaseUnit.Dimension
extends java.lang.Object

Author:
Dewey Dunnington Stores SI units for dimensions. A prime number is assigned to each dimension, so that when multiplied/divided in a more complex unit, a unique double is created for that combination of dimensions.
